name: chikorita
flavorText: A sweet aromagently wafts fromthe leaf on itshead. It is docileand loves to soakup the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
flavorText: The scent ofspices comes fromaround its neck.Somehow, sniffingit makes you wantto fight.

name: meganium
flavorText: The aroma thatrises from itspetals contains asubstance thatcalms aggressivefeelings.

name: cyndaquil
flavorText: It has a timid nature. If it is startled, the flames onits back burn more vigorously.

name: quilava
flavorText: Be careful if itturns its backduring battle. Itmeans that it willattack with thefire on its back.

name: typhlosion
flavorText: If its rage peaks,it becomes so hotthat anything thattouches it willinstantly goup in flames.

name: totodile
flavorText: Its well-developedjaws are powerfuland capable ofcrushing anything.Even its trainermust be careful.

name: croconaw
flavorText: If it loses afang, a new onegrows back in itsplace. There arealways 48 fangslining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
flavorText: When it bites withits massive andpowerful jaws, itshakes its headand savagely tearsits victim up.

name: sentret
flavorText: A very cautiousPOKéMON, it raisesitself up usingits tail to get abetter view of itssurroundings.

name: furret
flavorText: It makes a nest tosuit its long andskinny body. Thenest is impossiblefor other POKéMONto enter.

name: hoothoot
flavorText: It always standson one foot. Itchanges feet sofast, the movementcan rarely beseen.

name: noctowl
flavorText: Its eyes arespecially adapted.They concentrateeven faint lightand enable it tosee in the dark.

name: ledyba
flavorText: It is very timid.It will be afraidto move if it isalone. But it willbe active if it isin a group.

name: ledian
flavorText: When the starsflicker in thenight sky, itflutters about,scattering aglowing powder.

name: spinarak
flavorText: It lies still inthe same pose fordays in its web,waiting for itsunsuspecting preyto wander close.

name: ariados
flavorText: It spins stringnot only from itsrear but also fromits mouth. It ishard to tell whichend is which.

name: crobat
flavorText: It flies so si­lently through thedark on its fourwings that it maynot be noticedeven when nearby.

name: chinchou
flavorText: Chinchou blink their shining antennae at oneanother to claim their respective turf.

name: lanturn
flavorText: The light it emitsis so bright thatit can illuminatethe sea's surfacefrom a depth ofover three miles.

name: pichu
flavorText: It is not yetskilled at storingelectricity.It may send out ajolt if amusedor startled.

name: cleffa
flavorText: Because of itsunusual, star-likesilhouette, peoplebelieve that itcame here ona meteor.

name: igglybuff
flavorText: It has a very softbody. If it startsto roll, it willbounce all overand be impossibleto stop.

name: togepi
flavorText: The shell seems tobe filled withjoy. It is saidthat it will sharegood luck whentreated kindly.

name: togetic
flavorText: They say that itwill appear beforekindhearted, car­ing people andshower them withhappiness.

name: natu
flavorText: Because its wingsaren't yet fullygrown, it has tohop to get around.It is always star­ing at something.

name: xatu
flavorText: They say that itstays still andquiet because itis seeing both thepast and future atthe same time.

name: mareep
flavorText: If static elec­tricity builds inits body, itsfleece doubles involume. Touchingit will shock you.

name: flaaffy
flavorText: As a result ofstoring too muchelectricity, itdeveloped patcheswhere even downywool won't grow.

name: ampharos
flavorText: The tail's tipshines brightlyand can be seenfrom far away. Itacts as a beaconfor lost people.

name: bellossom
flavorText: Plentiful in the tropics. When itdances, its petals rub together andmake a pleasant ringing sound.

name: marill
flavorText: The tip of itstail, which con­tains oil that islighter than wa­ter, lets it swimwithout drowning.

name: azumarill
flavorText: It lives in water virtually all day long.Its body color and pattern act ascamouflage that makes it tough forenemies to spot in water.

name: sudowoodo
flavorText: Although it alwayspretends to be atree, its composi­tion appears to becloser to a rockthan a plant.

name: politoed
flavorText: If POLIWAG andPOLIWHIRL hear itsechoing cry, theyrespond by gather­ing from far andwide.

name: hoppip
flavorText: To keep from beingblown away by thewind, they gatherin clusters. Theydo enjoy gentlebreezes, though.

name: skiploom
flavorText: The bloom on topof its head opensand closes as thetemperature fluc­tuates up anddown.

name: jumpluff
flavorText: Once it catchesthe wind, it deft­ly controls itscotton-puff sporesto float, evenaround the world.

name: aipom
flavorText: Its tail is sopowerful that itcan use it to graba tree branch andhold itself up inthe air.

name: sunkern
flavorText: It may drop out ofthe sky suddenly.If attacked by aSPEAROW, it willviolently shakeits leaves.

name: sunflora
flavorText: It converts sun­light into energy.In the darknessafter sunset, itcloses its petalsand becomes still.

name: yanma
flavorText: If it flaps itswings really fast,it can generateshock waves thatwill shatter win­dows in the area.

name: wooper
flavorText: This POKéMON livesin cold water. Itwill leave thewater to searchfor food when itgets cold outside.

name: quagsire
flavorText: This carefreePOKéMON has aneasy-going nature.While swimming, italways bumps intoboat hulls.

name: espeon
flavorText: It uses the finehair that coversits body to senseair currents andpredict its ene­my's actions.

name: umbreon
flavorText: When agitated,this POKéMON pro­tects itself byspraying poisonoussweat from itspores.

name: murkrow
flavorText: Feared and loathedby many, it isbelieved to bringmisfortune to allthose who see itat night.

name: slowking
flavorText: It has incredibleintellect and in­tuition. Whateverthe situation, itremains calm andcollected.

name: misdreavus
flavorText: It likes playingmischievous trickssuch as screamingand wailing tostartle people atnight.

name: unown
flavorText: Their shapes looklike hieroglyphson ancient tab­lets. It is saidthat the two aresomehow related.

name: wobbuffet
flavorText: It hates light andshock. If attack­ed, it inflatesits body to pumpup its counter­strike.

name: girafarig
flavorText: Its tail has asmall brain of itsown. Beware! Ifyou get close, itmay react to yourscent and bite.

name: pineco
flavorText: It likes to makeits shell thickerby adding layersof tree bark. Theadditional weightdoesn't bother it.

name: forretress
flavorText: Its entire body isshielded by asteel-hard shell.What lurks insidethe armor is atotal mystery.

name: dunsparce
flavorText: When spotted, thisPOKéMON escapesbackward by furi­ously boring intothe ground withits tail.

name: gligar
flavorText: It flies straightat its target'sface then clampsdown on the star­tled victim toinject poison.

name: steelix
flavorText: It is thought its body transformedas a result of iron accumulatinginternally from swallowing soil.

name: snubbull
flavorText: Although it looksfrightening, it isactually kind andaffectionate. Itis very popularamong women.

name: granbull
flavorText: It is actuallytimid and easilyspooked. If at­tacked, it flailsabout to fend offits attacker.

name: qwilfish
flavorText: To fire its poisonspikes, it mustinflate its bodyby drinking over2.6 gallons ofwater all at once.

name: scizor
flavorText: It has a steel-hard body. Itintimidates foes by upraising itseye-patterned pincers.

name: shuckle
flavorText: The BERRIES itstores in itsvase-like shelldecompose andbecome a gooeyliquid.

name: heracross
flavorText: It is usually docile, but if it isdisturbed while sipping honey,it chases off the intruder with its horn.

name: sneasel
flavorText: Its paws concealsharp claws. Ifattacked, it sud­denly extends theclaws and startlesits enemy.

name: teddiursa
flavorText: If it finds honey,its crescent markglows. It alwayslicks its pawsbecause they aresoaked with honey.

name: ursaring
flavorText: Although it is agood climber, itprefers to snaptrees with itsforelegs and eatfallen BERRIES.

name: slugma
flavorText: It never sleeps.It has to keepmoving because ifit stopped, itsmagma body wouldcool and harden.

name: magcargo
flavorText: The shell on itsback is just skinthat has cooledand hardened. Itbreaks easily witha slight touch.

name: swinub
flavorText: It rubs its snouton the ground tofind and dig upfood. It sometimesdiscovers hotsprings.

name: piloswine
flavorText: Because the longhair all over itsbody obscures itssight, it justkeeps chargingrepeatedly.

name: corsola
flavorText: It continuouslysheds and grows.The tip of itshead is prized asa treasure for itsbeauty.

name: remoraid
flavorText: It has superb ac­curacy. The waterit shoots out canstrike even movingprey from morethan 300 feet.

name: octillery
flavorText: It traps enemieswith its suction-cupped tentaclesthen smashes themwith its rock-hardhead.

name: delibird
flavorText: It carries foodall day long.There are talesabout lost peoplewho were saved bythe food it had.

name: mantine
flavorText: As it majesticallyswims, it doesn'tcare if REMORAIDattach to it forscavenging itsleftovers.

name: skarmory
flavorText: Its sturdy wingslook heavy, butthey are actuallyhollow and light,allowing it to flyfreely in the sky.

name: houndour
flavorText: It uses differentkinds of cries forcommunicating withothers of its kindand for pursuingits prey.

name: houndoom
flavorText: If you are burnedby the flames itshoots from itsmouth, the painwill never goaway.

name: kingdra
flavorText: It is said that itusually hides inunderwater caves.It can createwhirlpools byyawning.

name: phanpy
flavorText: It swings its longsnout around play­fully, but becauseit is so strong,that can be dan­gerous.

name: donphan
flavorText: It has sharp, hardtusks and a ruggedhide. Its TACKLEis strong enoughto knock down ahouse.

name: porygon2
flavorText: This upgradedversion of PORYGONis designed forspace exploration.It can't fly,though.

name: stantler
flavorText: The curved antlerssubtly change theflow of air tocreate a strangespace where real­ity is distorted.

name: smeargle
flavorText: A special fluidoozes from the tipof its tail. Itpaints the fluideverywhere to markits territory.

name: tyrogue
flavorText: It is alwaysbursting with en­ergy. To make it­self stronger, itkeeps on fightingeven if it loses.

name: hitmontop
flavorText: If you becomeenchanted by itssmooth, elegant,dance-like kicks,you may getdrilled hard.

name: smoochum
flavorText: Its lips are themost sensitiveparts on its body.It always uses itslips first toexamine things.

name: elekid
flavorText: It rotates itsarms to generateelectricity, butit tires easily,so it charges uponly a little bit.

name: magby
flavorText: Each and everytime it inhalesand exhales, hotembers dribble outof its mouth andnostrils.

name: miltank
flavorText: Its milk is packedwith nutrition,making it theultimate beveragefor the sick orweary.

name: blissey
flavorText: Anyone who takeseven one bite ofBLISSEY's egg be­comes unfailinglycaring and pleas­ant to everyone.

name: raikou
flavorText: The rain clouds itcarries let itfire thunderboltsat will. They saythat it descendedwith lightning.

name: entei
flavorText: Volcanoes eruptwhen it barks. Un­able to restrainits extreme power,it races headlongaround the land.

name: suicune
flavorText: It races around the world topurify fouled water. It dashesaway with the north wind.

name: larvitar
flavorText: It feeds on soil.After it has eatena large mountain,it will fallasleep so it cangrow.

name: pupitar
flavorText: Its shell is ashard as sheetrock, and it isalso very strong.Its THRASHING cantopple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
flavorText: Its body can't beharmed by any sortof attack, so itis very eager tomake challengesagainst enemies.

name: lugia
flavorText: It is said that itquietly spends itstime deep at thebottom of the seabecause its powersare too strong.

name: ho-oh
flavorText: Legends claim thisPOKéMON flies theworld's skies con­tinuously on itsmagnificent seven-colored wings.

name: celebi
flavorText: This POKéMON wan­ders across time.Grass and treesflourish in theforests in whichit has appeared.
